<p rend="centre"> Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</p>

<p rend="nikaya">Khuddakanikāye</p>

<p rend="book">Khuddakapāṭhapāḷi</p>

<p rend="chapter">1. Saraṇattayaṃ</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Buddhaṃ <pb ed="M" n="0.0001" /><pb ed="V" n="0.0001" /><pb ed="P" n="0.0001" /><pb ed="T" n="0.0001" /> saraṇaṃ gacchāmi;</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Saṅghaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Dutiyampi buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi;</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Dutiyampi dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Dutiyampi saṅghaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Tatiyampi <pb ed="V" n="0.0002" /> buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi;</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Tatiyampi dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Tatiyampi saṅghaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi.</p>

<p rend="centre">Saraṇattayaṃ <note>saraṇagamanaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ (syā.)</note> niṭṭhitaṃ.</p>
